{"tid":277913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鼠王芬暗串蔣麗芸：訓練貓不如訓練人","createTime":"2017-06-10T04:46:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-18T11:35:53.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0aa91cf72ded0348b5b7946b90b1e2aff7c735cf","tid":277913,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T04:46:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170610/large/1497067108_fb36.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170610%2Flarge%2F1497067108_fb36.jpg&h=5560f3fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蔣麗芸周三於立法會提出口頭質詢，建議食物及環境衞生署仿傚外國，組織流浪貓成為「社區貓隻滅鼠隊」，協助解決鼠患問題，但食衞局局長高永文認為，流浪貓有一定的傳播疾病風險，需要進一步研究。因治理九龍西鼠患而有「鼠王芬」之名的立法會議員梁美芬昨晚在Facebook發帖，留下標籤「#訓練貓不如訓練人」，又再重申希望「區區有鼠王」。<br />\n<br />\n梁美芬昨晚在Facebook發帖指，深水埗及旺角的最新鼠患指數已分別達8.9%及8.4%，反映鼠患問題嚴重，「家吓睇老鼠唔使特登去迪迪尼喇」。她又呼籲，「其他區嘅議員加把勁啦」，希望十八區都有「鼠王」，「群策群力，一齊治鼠，睇下啲老鼠仲有冇得到處開party！」。<br />\n不過，該篇帖文卻留下標籤「#訓練貓不如訓練人」，暗諷蔣麗芸的組織流浪貓滅鼠隊不可行；又特別標籤了無黨派議員毛孟靜及新民黨葉劉淑儀，「#到時Regina Ip 葉劉淑儀姐姐唔使淨係識得搵鼠王芬妹妹喇」。"},{"pid":"d537d3fb6bdff77fc653858dee31e6886e3efbd5","tid":277913,"uid":53105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T04:51:25.000Z","msg":"打和"},{"pid":"6537ad39489647c8fba810fcb2dec0ecaa273dbe","tid":277913,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T05:20:57.000Z","msg":"不如訓練catgirl<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0368a84c07dde82dd6aef2bb3f415115a67e4a2f","tid":277913,"uid":50719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T05:32:52.000Z","msg":"老鼠專家"},{"pid":"54248e30b4978a382b4c0c18ffb556e6ce6f90cd","tid":277913,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T05:33:52.000Z","msg":"其實佢兩派不和左好耐啦"},{"pid":"e3f13caf1580b8989178c706e88d09542a80ca33","tid":277913,"uid":74012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T09:06:56.000Z","msg":"佢老叫落過手去滅老鼠<br />\n<br />\n蔣麗芸就得把口鳩噏，你擺流浪貓係街捉老鼠, 邊個負責餵貓同埋執貓屎呀？"},{"pid":"4d4668581e2f0d27426123932888be7ca188a949","tid":277913,"uid":37524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T09:34:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打和</blockquote><br />\n叫李慧瓊做和事老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bfb285285d4e2ac7176ba19464f2c9c50726a89","tid":277913,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T11:28:38.000Z","msg":"梁美芬係隻老鼠"},{"pid":"75e186ff8a7f4e52bcb0b47038805e5e7d5bc21d","tid":277913,"uid":32723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T11:35:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>打和</blockquote><br />\n叫李慧瓊做和事老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n諗起都嘈呀"}]}